<abstract><t>In-situ Operations, Administration, and Maintenance (IOAM) records operational and telemetry information in the packet while the packet traverses a path between two points in the network.  This document presents new flags in the IOAM Trace Option headers.  Specifically, the document defines the Loopback and Active flags.</t></abstract>

